= Fiscal Policy

Tax policy involves issues of taxation (WIP).

Tax Deduction 1 DESC (WIP)

- @union_deductions1
- @union_deductions2
- @upper_class_charity_deduction
- @upper_class_welfare_deduction
- @impoverished_tax_exemption
- @volunteering_credit: Provide tax credits for people volunteering in registered organisations
- @new_business_credit: Provide tax credits for newly-establsihed small businesses
- @cooperatives_credit: Provide tax credits for all co-operatives
- @root: Do not change the tax system.
- @easy_discard
- @cancel_advisor_action

@union_deductions1
title: Provide tax deductions for union dues
subtitle: -0.5 budget
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough budget
choose-if: budget >= 0.5
view-if: (trun_ind_perc + trun_nmc_perc + trun_rur_perc + iww_ind_perc + iww_nmc_perc + iww_rur_perc + iww_unm_perc + chrun_tot_perc) < 0.12 and union_ddcs = 0
on-arrival: budget -= 0.5; trun_ind_perc += 0.03; trun_nmc_perc += 0.007; trun_rur_perc += 0.015; iww_ind_perc += 0.004 if syndicalism = 1; iww_nmc_perc += 0.003 if syndicalism = 1; iww_rur_perc += 0.003 if syndicalism = 1; iww_unm_perc += 0.004 if syndicalism = 1; chrun_tot_perc += 0.02; union_ddcs = 1;

Description

@union_deductions2
title: Provide tax deductions for union dues
subtitle: -1 budget
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough budget
choose-if: budget >= 1
view-if: (trun_ind_perc + trun_nmc_perc + trun_rur_perc + iww_ind_perc + iww_nmc_perc + iww_rur_perc + iww_unm_perc + chrun_tot_perc) > 0.12 and union_ddcs = 0
on-arrival: budget -= 1; trun_ind_perc += 0.015; trun_nmc_perc += 0.009; trun_rur_perc += 0.03; iww_ind_perc += 0.006 if syndicalism = 1; iww_nmc_perc += 0.004 if syndicalism = 1; iww_rur_perc += 0.006 if syndicalism = 1; iww_unm_perc += 0.007 if syndicalism = 1; chrun_tot_perc += 0.03;

Description

@upper_class_charity_deduction
title: Provide tax deductions for donating to charities
subtitle: -1.5 budget
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough budget
choose-if: budget >= 1.5
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: budget -= 1.5; charity += 2; new_middle_spd += 4; old_middle_spd += 4; unemployed_spd += 2; left_dissent += 8; center_dissent += 6; labour_dissent += 2; dvp_left += 2; ddp_left += 4; lvp_left += 3; ddp_relation += 10; dvp_relation += 7; z_relation += 5; kpd_relation -= 12; ddp_cohesion += 1; inflation += 0.2; economic_growth += 0.2;

description

@upper_class_welfare_deduction 
title: [? if ucwddc = 0 : Provide a tax deduction for donating to the welfare fund ?] [? if ucwddc = 1 : Increase the deduction for donating to welfare ?]
subtitle: -1 budget
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough budget
choose-if: budget >= 1
max-visits: 2
on-arrival: welfare_cost -= 0.25 if ucwddc = 0; welfare_cost -= 0.15 if ucwddc = 1; z_relation += 3; ddp_relation += 3; dvp_relation += 3; ddp_left += 1; dvp_left += 1; lvp_left += 1; left_dissent += 4; center_dissent += 2; labour_dissent -= 2; reformist_dissent -= 4;

description

